<p>
My research interests are in Programming Languages and Methodologies,
Object-Oriented Programming, Mathematical Logic and
Open and Distance Learning (may be you like better the term <EM>eLearning</EM>...).
</p>

<p>
I have been working or work on
<ul>
<li> the use of logic for course configuration in distance learning;</li>

<li>the definition of a specialization inheritance
mechanism for object-oriented programming languages and
the use of inheritance in distributed object-oriented programming,</li>
<li>
the axiomatization of <i>map calculus</i>.</li>
</ul>
</p>

